name: Spiritum Portals - Sandscape
description: White Sands. A mystical beach. The remnants of an ancient sea amidst the mountains, used as a nuclear missile test range -- surely the lore of White Sands is a peek into the history they would have us believe. Let the crystally whites, the lone cacti, the hazy sandstorms, and the purple dusk of White Sands be a portal into the true reality.
